      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must be compared against experimental measurements using a quantitative metric (e.g., E% or U95) at all validated operating points.",
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison was performed at three operating points with E% reported. Systematic over-prediction of 18–22% was observed at high-speed low-flow conditions; two points lacked experimental reference data."
