    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to support the intended use. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed and hemolysis predictions were within acceptable bounds at the primary operating point. Several factors were not fully assessed; however, the team judged the residual uncertainty to be acceptable given the available validation evidence and the conservative nature of the hemolysis model.",
